Package org.jcvi.jillion.fasta.qual

This package deals with Fasta files that contain QualitySequence data.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    QualityFastaDataStore
    QualityFastaDataStoreis a FastaDataStore for storing PhredQualitys.
    QualityFastaRecord  
    QualityFastaWriter  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractQualityFastaRecordVisitor
    AbstractQualityFastaRecordVisitor is an abstract implementation of FastaRecordVisitor that will collect the visit methods for a single fasta record and build an instance of QualityFastaRecord.
    QualityFastaFileDataStoreBuilder
    QualityFastaFileDataStoreBuilder is a factory class that can create new instances of QualityFastaDataStores using data from a given input fasta file.
    QualityFastaRecordBuilder
    QualityFastaRecordBuilder is a factory class that makes instances of QualityFastaRecords.
    QualityFastaWriterBuilder
    QualityFastaWriterBuilder builds a new instance of QualityFastaWriter that will write fasta encoded quality data to the provided File or OutputStream.
